Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.91,0:21:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.93,0:21:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…怎么说好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…我不想等明天
